sequenceDiagram
  participant S as Smartwatch sensors (110)
  participant A as AI / BAC module (120)
  participant B as Secure BLE link (140)
  participant V as Vehicle module (150)
  S->>A: 1. Continuous sensor data
  Note over A: 2. Estimate BAC, compare to 0.08 g/dL
  A->>B: 3. BAC status packet (30 s)
  B->>V: 4. Deliver status
  Note over V: 5. Block ignition (default fail-safe)
  V-->>B: 6. Override attempt
  B->>A: 7. Request verification
  A->>S: 8. Request BAC recheck
  S->>A: 9. Fresh sensor data
  A->>V: 10. Maintain ignition block
